OL,3,CSpringhill, Westrock massacre inquest
OL,4,Cfindings to be delivered
OL,6,FA coroner is due to deliver findings
OL,7,Flater today following an inquest into
OL,8,Fthe fatal shooting of five civilians
OL,9,Fby the British Army in west Belfast
OL,10,Fmore than 50 years ago.
OL,12,FThe victims ` a priest and three
OL,13,Fteenagers among them ` were killed in
OL,14,Fthe Springhill and Westrock areas on 9
OL,15,FJuly 1972.
OL,17,FThose who died were Father Noel
OL,18,FFitzpatrick, 42, Patrick Butler, 38,
OL,19,FJohn Dougal, 16, David McCafferty, 15,
OL,20,Fand Margaret Gargan, 13.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
