OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1777539988
OL,3,CSpringhill, Westrock massacre inquest
OL,4,Cfindings to be delivered
OL,6,FFamilies and friends are expected to
OL,7,Fgather at Belfast Coroner's Court for
OL,8,Fthe long-awaited outcome.
OL,10,FThe inquest concluded in April 2024,
OL,11,Fjust hours before the former
OL,12,FGovernment's guillotine on conflict-
OL,13,Frelated court cases as part of new
OL,14,Flegacy laws came into effect.
OL,16,FIt was the last of the coronial
OL,17,Finvestigations into Troubles-related
OL,18,Fdeaths completed before the May 1
OL,19,Fdeadline of the Legacy Act, which is
OL,20,Fcurrently being reviewed under the
OL,21,FLabour government.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
