CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1777539988
OL,3,CSpringhill, Westrock massacre inquest
OL,4,Cfindings to be delivered
OL,6,FIt had been a fresh inquest ordered by
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's attorney general in
OL,8,F2014 after an original inquest in 1973
OL,9,Freturned an open verdict.
OL,11,FIn a joint statement, the Butler,
OL,12,FGargan, Dougal and McCafferty families
OL,13,Fsaid they "stand together after almost
OL,14,F54 years of grief, loss, and
OL,15,Funanswered questions".
OL,17,F"The deaths of our loved ones that
OL,18,Foccurred at Springhill and Westrock on
OL,19,F9th July 1972 have cast a long shadow
OL,20,Fover our lives," they said.
OL,26,@uD@KOUwD@UO]yD@AOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
