OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1777539988
OL,3,CSpringhill, Westrock massacre inquest
OL,4,Cfindings to be delivered
OL,6,F"Each of those who died was an
OL,7,Findividual ` deeply loved and still
OL,8,Fdeeply missed.
OL,10,F"For us, this is not history; it is
OL,11,Fsomething we have lived with every day.
OL,13,F"We have consistently maintained that
OL,14,Fthose who died were innocent
OL,15,Fcivilians, and that the force used on
OL,16,Fthat day was indiscriminate and
OL,17,Funjustified.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
