FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1777539988
OL,3,CSpringhill, Westrock massacre inquest
OL,4,Cfindings to be delivered
OL,6,F"For over five decades, our families
OL,7,Fhave raised serious concerns that
OL,8,Fthose initial investigations failed to
OL,9,Fproperly establish the truth.
OL,11,F"We now await the coroner Justice
OL,12,FSchofield's findings.
OL,14,F"We do so with both hope and
OL,15,Fapprehension` hope that the findings
OL,16,Fwill reflect the full circumstances of
OL,17,Fwhat happened, and apprehension
OL,18,Fbecause of the weight this moment
OL,19,Fcarries for all of our families."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@AOU{D@aO]
